<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Case Creation Confirmation</title>
    <style>
         body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .case-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .case-info table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .case-info th, .case-info td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .case-info th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="main-body">
    <div class="container">
<div class="header">
            <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/xT6tSdGJ/Ecosync.png" alt="ECO SYNC Logo">
        </div>
        <h1>Case Creation Confirmation</h1>
        <p>Dear {!Case.SuppliedName},</p>
        <p>We have received your case and it has been successfully created. Below are the details:</p>
        <div class="case-info">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Case Number</th>
                    <td>{!Case.CaseNumber}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Case Message</th>
                    <td>{!Case.Description}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <td>{!Case.SuppliedName}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We will review your case and get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email is generated automatically. Please do not reply.</p>
            <p>For any further assistance, please visit <a href="https://agno-dev-ed.develop.my.site.com/CFC2024/s">ECOSYNC</a> or contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>